{"tid":1660354,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"日大學選美驚現「146cm蘿莉」！空靈系小隻馬引網暴動：戀愛惹~","createTime":"2019-10-17T12:44:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T17:00:08.000Z","uid":32511,"like":11,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"53e6ab9973969236b63d4260515511583481571f","tid":1660354,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T12:44:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4zNdqaw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4zNdqaw.jpg&h=aa360749&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本各大學每年到了年底都會舉辦校園「正妹型男選拔」，今年東京女子大學校園美女的5位候選人當中，出現一名個子超級嬌小的蘿莉，看起來就像國中生誤入比賽，而她可愛的外貌引起大批網友暴動，紛紛為她拜票。<br />\n <br />\n東京女子大學日前於推特公布5名進入決選的候選人，其中，這名只有146公分的3號候選人大渕野野花（大渕野々花）就站在宣傳照的正中央，特別顯眼，照片也因此呈現了完美的「凹字型」。她近日在個人推特中拉票，不忘開玩笑吐槽自己「簡直就是著名的公開處刑」。不過，這個身高卻讓許多熱愛「小隻女」的男性而言為之瘋狂。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OtBxFJ2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOtBxFJ2.jpg&h=bf97d16a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JaHtd33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJaHtd33.jpg&h=a9337695&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年已經19歲的大渕野野花目前就讀於日本文學專攻2年級，未來目標是當上一名女主播，她除了個子相當嬌小以外，臉蛋更像洋娃娃一樣精緻，擁有高挺的鼻樑以及櫻桃小嘴，笑起來還有明顯的臥蠶。大渕野野花也時常在推特中發布自己的日常照片，露出的甜美笑容更是融化許多男粉絲。<br />\n <br />\n目前東京女子大學校園美女的決賽投票尚未結束，投票結果將會在11月公開。不少網友看到大渕野野花的照片後都紛紛暴動，直呼「太可愛了」、「已戀愛」、「這真的成年了嗎」、「這麼可愛當然要幫她拜一下票」、「看起來真的太萌啦！」、「莫名激發濃厚的保護欲」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nmdj5a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNmdj5a1.jpg&h=83c9ba3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/miss_twcu193/status/1168286198147641345\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmiss_twcu193%2Fstatus%2F1168286198147641345&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAd6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=fd80749b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmiss_twcu193%2Fstatus%2F1168286198147641345&h=5a2d5f49\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/miss_twcu193/status/1168286198147641345</a>"},{"pid":"20d6d3e1062703a0d7edebd34b500292e3d9d7db","tid":1660354,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T12:44:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/afoWPNY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FafoWPNY.jpg&h=041452ea&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"1ce7b0c68910bcceffbeff1c434a8461f2cd6de2","tid":1660354,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T12:45:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a511a8db1b3685aad8e4c49b265b92dac82dec0a","tid":1660354,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T12:48:16.000Z","msg":"好可愛呀呀呀呀呀"},{"pid":"b37a54e52281a35478c80bb80d6a13eb38b18218","tid":1660354,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T12:48:21.000Z","msg":"抱返屋企無難度"},{"pid":"4bf29df769fc68efff478206c7cbf8db4089e5b0","tid":1660354,"uid":5921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T12:48:27.000Z","msg":"合法loli<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb5ff4c227037ade060b1f4392ec82646c6a1bc9","tid":1660354,"uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b37a54e52281a35478c80bb80d6a13eb38b18218","tid":1660354,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T12:48:21.000Z","msg":"抱返屋企無難度"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T12:49:13.000Z","msg":"又真係冇難度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b289bfec4dba9a86769aa8b0a4adf67ec37a43e","tid":1660354,"uid":193951,"like":8,"dislike":0